PAID COLLABORATION💸 GUIDE. Comment “rate” to receive rate card AND email template directly in your dm. And to use that template well, read this 👇🏼 

1. Know Your Worth- For eg: if you have 5k followers, 8k average views on every reel, charge a minimum of Rs1,000. 

2. Brand’s size- 
•  if it’s small/startup- speaking from a business perspective, you need to charge a good amount since they don’t have much to bring you in terms of reach/ brand value just yet. 
•  If it’s big/ corporate- charge lower than startups as it’s benefiting your portfolio too!

3. Charge for Deliverables in the order - reel>ugc video>carousel>static>story. (exact details in the template link)

4. Usage rights- Charge extra if they want to reuse content to run ads on platforms like facebook, website etc.
 
5. Exclusivity - charge extra if the brand dosent allow you to work with competitor brands. That’s lost opportunity for you = charge more.

5. Content Quality & Time Investment
	•	dslr>phone shoot, high end edits> simple edits, scripting provided> do it yourself, location costs, voiceover, etc

6.Rush fees
	•	Is the brand asking for urgent delivery (24–48 hrs)? 

FINAL CHARGE: 
For example: use a Base Rate + Add-ons Model
5k base for 1 reel
	•	1k for 1 month usage rights
	•	2k for collab on instagram
	•	500 rush fees
= 8.5k total charge

Bonus Tip:
✅ If you’re unsure, ask what their budget is and work backwards.
✅ Once the deal is confirmed, Confirm it with an email mentioning the other details. (mentioned in the template link)

Comment down any questions you have and SAVE this reel for later♥️
